<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="B客戶">
  <data key="d0">B客戶</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">B客戶 is a term used to denote a customer in the context of maintenance services. This entity represents the individual or organization that receives various forms of maintenance support. B客戶 is identified as the recipient of maintenance services, encompassing both current and past service provisions. The term is used to describe a customer for whom maintenance services are provided, are being provided, were provided, or will be performed. This indicates that B客戶 can be associated with maintenance activities at different stages—whether ongoing, completed, or yet to commence.

B客戶 is linked to specific maintenance records, suggesting a formal documentation process that tracks the services rendered to this customer. The term emphasizes the importance of maintaining detailed records for each customer to ensure efficient and effective service delivery. This association with maintenance records underscores the systematic approach taken in managing and documenting the services provided to B客戶.

The descriptions highlight several key aspects of B客戶's role, reinforcing that B客戶 is the customer for whom maintenance services were provided, are being provided, or will be performed. The consistent use of the term across different contexts underscores its significance in the maintenance service industry, where accurate record-keeping and timely service delivery are crucial.&lt;SEP&gt;B客戶is the customer for whom maintenance services are being performed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8c09713dbee86ef202f12b324af7f6ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daae99df44293b1fcd73d51d0a4ae1e4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7f07339628f6e485361398b8561f6b86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0c86783e48dde87530d3aaf96cd9b7eb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-151b86619aa7050e8f104c3774db92e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-872c3c21f69ec7e42b0977befb3dc3b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b9b15e91b000619dbd7585c483363c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79d68fc369433f9d13628ad2e1fbda89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39a6c5824a573b154841bea458b038e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba1a47d0d804edc13e2a4c9baa424968&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-339cd0fad5e54271b81a9c28f01d86c0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-079886f578cd8929a1d242f25342154d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec56bb4a8645a8e5c2970370436fecaa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8493d57e7d369ef59edc24c96f7e58da&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d92de8d6fd691fbaf5541adab0b5091b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3473c451b90313c144554b6252887062</data>
