<node id="A人員">
  <data key="d0">A人員</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">A人員 is an engineer primarily focused on performing a variety of maintenance tasks. This role encompasses confirming account permissions, managing service transfers, and conducting maintenance services, with a particular focus on activities related to Splunk. A人員's duties are crucial for ensuring the smooth operation and upkeep of systems, making them integral to the maintenance process.

A人員's involvement in maintenance is not limited to a single client; they are also involved in performing maintenance tasks for B客戶. This highlights their versatility and importance across different clients and systems. The consistent mention of A人員 as engineers underscores their technical expertise and the critical nature of their role in maintaining operational efficiency.

A人員's responsibilities include working on DEP02, backup scripts, PA reports, and system upgrades. These activities collectively emphasize that A人員 are essential for the upkeep and smooth functioning of various systems. Their range of maintenance activities contributes to the overall integrity and performance of the systems they support. Additionally, A人員 is involved in IP adjustments and software upgrades, further demonstrating their broad skill set and importance in maintaining system functionality.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8c09713dbee86ef202f12b324af7f6ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad2718858692ffab141bba894fc28562&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-347c6b40d1af0b5af1b3893cfa832073&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daae99df44293b1fcd73d51d0a4ae1e4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-036c671c1c1448c48546c94a566a944d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-63c0f1ad02d99fa02ad3bd3e653b71ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bffc830901e0a9ae907eeedba8c4b2a4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-151b86619aa7050e8f104c3774db92e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e72b71ff65672444ea31e031951b7067&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f16bbf8897730f8ea52e505eb23f9d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c4bd2a22d4e95b83f0a317d37ab5eeb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b7d5c8ea6bbab839645b2785588bd370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8daa3bb2e1adb74b0f2ae11979877a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-872c3c21f69ec7e42b0977befb3dc3b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cda5b194f64fdf543f0fb2d81d1de387&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b9b15e91b000619dbd7585c483363c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79d68fc369433f9d13628ad2e1fbda89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39a6c5824a573b154841bea458b038e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-def195f623c9020bab75365061c20c8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba1a47d0d804edc13e2a4c9baa424968&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b313720171028705758fc32b029efad0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-079886f578cd8929a1d242f25342154d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8493d57e7d369ef59edc24c96f7e58da&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-974c119c4e7ec9872d0c953bc6fdb366&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3de4536cfaa5fca4318dffcfe2778cde&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7a20797a65d83b4f057c17237dc42e31&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b95d3980924c2bf42d49243e106e188e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d92de8d6fd691fbaf5541adab0b5091b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3473c451b90313c144554b6252887062</data>
