<node id="10.0.2/2025.11.14">
  <data key="d0">10.0.2/2025.11.14</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">10.0.2/2025.11.14 is the latest version of a software system, released on November 14, 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;10.0.2/2025.11.14 is the latest version of the Splunk credit card processing system, recommended for update due to security concerns.&lt;SEP&gt;10.0.2/2025.11.14 is the latest version of Splunk, recommended for update to address security vulnerabilities.</data>
