<node id="A部門">
  <data key="d0">A部門</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">A部門 is a department with a broad range of responsibilities related to maintaining and managing various aspects of Splunk's infrastructure and user permissions. One of its key roles involves adjusting user permissions in Splunk and setting capability values for specific roles, such as maintainer and ess_analyst. This includes handling account inventory verification and reporting tasks, ensuring that all accounts are properly inventoried and reported to relevant parties like C同事.

Additionally, A部門 is tasked with maintaining account permissions and confirming service transfers, which involves verifying the accuracy of user access levels and ensuring smooth transitions when services are moved or reassigned. This department also plays a crucial role in checking report deliveries, making sure that all reports are sent out correctly and on time. For instance, they send reports to Hank as part of their account inventory and reporting tasks.

A部門 is also responsible for handling PA reports and related issues. This includes scheduling these reports and resolving any errors that may arise during the process. They address specific issues such as Splunk role capabilities and resending monthly PA reports when necessary. Their responsibilities extend to various maintenance tasks related to Splunk's infrastructure, ensuring that the system runs smoothly and efficiently.

In summary, A部門 is a multifaceted department that handles a wide array of tasks, from user permissions and account inventory to report management and infrastructure maintenance, all aimed at ensuring the smooth operation of Splunk and its associated services.&lt;SEP&gt;A部門is a department responsible for various Splunk-related tasks, including IP adjustments and software upgrades.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e8546250502508fe4fe37b7b73ba8a02&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daae99df44293b1fcd73d51d0a4ae1e4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79d68fc369433f9d13628ad2e1fbda89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39a6c5824a573b154841bea458b038e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e6c37810e998efc4976989502d405eb9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-62d5f33672911ac78bd672bf3fafca1b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-68f5e0388fd826eca73f7ba01f50ff1d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-079886f578cd8929a1d242f25342154d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8493d57e7d369ef59edc24c96f7e58da&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7a20797a65d83b4f057c17237dc42e31</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773392566</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="B部門">
  <data key="d0">B部門</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">B部門 is a specialized department responsible for a wide array of technical tasks. One of its primary responsibilities involves handling FISAC (Financial Information System for Accounting and Control) data, which includes accommodation, retrieval, and overall management. This encompasses ensuring the smooth operation of data systems and addressing any anomalies that may arise.

In addition to data management, B部門 is heavily involved in testing the SH KVstore engine. This includes identifying and resolving anomalies within the engine, as well as setting up LDAP (Lightweight Directory Access Protocol) configurations to ensure secure and efficient data access. The department also manages various maintenance activities related to these systems.

B部門 plays a crucial role in indexer management, particularly with the IDX cluster. This involves adding indexers to the cluster and monitoring their synchronization status to maintain optimal performance. The department is also responsible for tasks such as Centos OS upgrades and IP transfers, which are essential for maintaining the infrastructure's stability and security.

Furthermore, B部門 handles troubleshooting issues related to n8n and Splunk connectivity. This ensures that data flows seamlessly between different systems, enhancing overall operational efficiency. The department's responsibilities also include managing various other maintenance activities, ensuring that all technical aspects of their operations run smoothly.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e8546250502508fe4fe37b7b73ba8a02&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daae99df44293b1fcd73d51d0a4ae1e4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79d68fc369433f9d13628ad2e1fbda89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e6c37810e998efc4976989502d405eb9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-62d5f33672911ac78bd672bf3fafca1b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-68f5e0388fd826eca73f7ba01f50ff1d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-079886f578cd8929a1d242f25342154d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8493d57e7d369ef59edc24c96f7e58da&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7a20797a65d83b4f057c17237dc42e31</data>
