<node id="C人員">
  <data key="d0">C人員</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">C人員 are engineers who play a crucial role in various maintenance activities. They are primarily responsible for performing maintenance tasks, with a specific focus on supporting E客戶 and B客戶. Their duties include executing general maintenance tasks as well as more specialized tasks related to maintaining systems efficiently.

C人員 are involved in managing the Splunk Indexer queue, highlighting their role in both routine and technical aspects of maintenance. They assist with various tasks including KV store certificate updates and Splunk bundle storage issues. While some descriptions mention C人員 directly performing maintenance tasks, others note that they are engineers involved in maintenance services without specifying direct involvement in particular actions. This suggests that C人員 may have varying levels of engagement in different maintenance activities, depending on the context.

Additionally, there is a mention of C人員 being an engineer involved in the maintenance record but not directly involved in the described actions, which could imply administrative or supervisory roles within the maintenance team. Overall, C人員 are integral to ensuring the smooth operation and upkeep of systems through their expertise in maintenance services. They also receive reports from A部門, indicating a collaborative role within the organization.

The descriptions consistently emphasize that C人員 are engineers who perform maintenance tasks, particularly on E客戶's Splunk system. This reinforces their technical expertise and direct involvement in maintaining critical systems. Their roles encompass both hands-on maintenance activities and potentially administrative or supervisory functions, making them essential for the overall efficiency and reliability of the systems they support.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is another engineer involved in the maintenance service.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ad2718858692ffab141bba894fc28562&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb7c4c3c548295066f2e46951093db13&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daae99df44293b1fcd73d51d0a4ae1e4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d9302d9d184fdb9a6a2e82a94832acd4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7f07339628f6e485361398b8561f6b86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-877bba941bf057cea37bb476990c258b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0c86783e48dde87530d3aaf96cd9b7eb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-87a5d3bdc7f7ced7e1e84c3bd0d56953&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c959468d5f0324d8fb4b077c1bb96403&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fc30dcc322140323c8bfe6b14b0d13ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45f16bbf8897730f8ea52e505eb23f9d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c4bd2a22d4e95b83f0a317d37ab5eeb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-872c3c21f69ec7e42b0977befb3dc3b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cda5b194f64fdf543f0fb2d81d1de387&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b9b15e91b000619dbd7585c483363c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79d68fc369433f9d13628ad2e1fbda89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b74582c30b69f701a3da6ea6d4172cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8532e183ea92bf2dc78eb5db5d132f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39a6c5824a573b154841bea458b038e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b3e82ffed91f34651149d2b379bf0f5d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba1a47d0d804edc13e2a4c9baa424968&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-339cd0fad5e54271b81a9c28f01d86c0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c832993149432df5dc6036fe178953c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8df58b4e9708dc04ffb7b8f3601ce86a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-236858901881e8e94fc17b2ea00afa5b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b95f91639c99de7f8e53b56f8d3034f8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3e8bcbc18db568bb24e7e1eab887cb9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-31c18a0b19e8cf12abfc0e16e21a563c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-079886f578cd8929a1d242f25342154d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec56bb4a8645a8e5c2970370436fecaa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fbe581137695748adecf47766d8576d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8493d57e7d369ef59edc24c96f7e58da&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc1d666b949d461ffee4c06b27c1ca07&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1c4c9f70d8a60c1c0ca8dbbfa4baa1f5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-16690bcfdcdb6d8c3312a19fe520352e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7a20797a65d83b4f057c17237dc42e31&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b95d3980924c2bf42d49243e106e188e</data>
