  <data key="d2">The version update involves upgrading from the current version 9.3.8 to the latest version 10.0.2 due to security vulnerabilities.&lt;SEP&gt;The version update involves upgrading from 9.3.3/2025.02.26 to 10.0.2/2025.11.14 due to vulnerabilities in the current version.&lt;SEP&gt;The current version of Splunk is 9.3.8, and the latest version available is 10.0.2. No update is recommended due to the absence of major vulnerabilities or bugs.&lt;SEP&gt;The current version of Splunk is 9.3.3, released on 2025.02.26, with a recommendation to update to the latest version 10.0.0, released on 2025.07.28.&lt;SEP&gt;The current version of the Splunk system is 9.3.8, released on 2025.11.14, with a recommendation to upgrade to version 10.0.2 due to security vulnerabilities.</data>
